1. Čovek je slobodni* da radi šta god poželi. (The man is free to do whatever he wishes.)
2. Slobodni* od bilo kakvih obaveza, on je mogao da odluta gde god želi. (Free from any obligations, he was able to wander wherever he wanted.)
3. Slobodno* vreme je najdragocenije što imamo. (Free time is the most precious thing we have.)
4. Slobodan* da bira svoju sudbinu, on se opredelio da uči strani jezik. (Free to choose his fate, he decided to learn a foreign language.)
5. Slobodna* u svojim mislima, ona je mogla da se razvija. (Free in her thoughts, she was able to develop.)